<title>USA: Bassett Furniture sets special qtly div.</title>
<headline>Bassett Furniture sets special qtly div.</headline>
<dateline>BASSETT, Virgina 1997-02-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>Bassett Furniture Industries Inc said Wednesday its board of directors had approved a special dividend of $0.20 a share in addition to its regular quarterly dividend of the same amount.  </p>
<p>The company said it will pay the special dividend on March 7 to shareholders of record March 3.</p>
<p>&quot;This Special Dividend is intended to reflect the returns earned on the company's investment portfolio,&quot; it said.</p>
<p>It said it will also pay the regular dividend under the same terms.</p>
<p>((-- New York Newsroom, 212-859-1610))</p>
